{"tid":1735442,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Popo 的下場。","createTime":"2019-11-18T14:38:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T18:32:53.000Z","uid":73055,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3e3cd69f2b748947b103b5ece35fcf3edaed45eb","tid":1735442,"uid":73055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T14:38:11.000Z","msg":"狗們全身暗病check唔到，清算完畢後焗住出黎搵食；冇得借病呃綜援。全世界都知你地係狗，所以黃藍鋪都拒絕聘請。啲狗被迫賣身，接親都係帶性病嘅古寒美極級客人。<br />\n<br />\n至於親狗呢，狗爸媽嫲爺婆公都長命百歲但百病纏身，淨係可以依靠班狗照顧。咁狗仔女呢就全部死於非命，要白頭狗送黑頭狗。就算仔女死曬狗嫂想再生，狗嫂次次都會臨盤先胎死腹中，而狗嫂次次都會救得翻。啲狗就算想尋死都唔會成功，次次臨死先比人救翻上黎。冇事冇幹第日繼續翻工（有良心的真&middot;勇/和家屬則豁免以上命運）。"},{"pid":"b98a637b3488cb802b83ba785e88d1b7d1e4f76b","tid":1735442,"uid":73055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T14:39:36.000Z","msg":"榮光借歸香港呀仆街"},{"pid":"abb218ac3fa43c965c12341f97e3fbd56ecd2e9e","tid":1735442,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T14:40:26.000Z","msg":"[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6e2243e023fb79a1dea7c6dd9c411101f9739fe7","tid":1735442,"uid":258598,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T14:42:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7391580a87e3655b906b9bb905cb8e38ffcc6f80","tid":1735442,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T14:51:40.000Z","msg":"condom用完唔通會留低做紀念咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45daaead120bdea1739fd9187d064f705257cbe2","tid":1735442,"uid":73055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6e2243e023fb79a1dea7c6dd9c411101f9739fe7","tid":1735442,"uid":258598,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T14:42:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T15:15:32.000Z","msg":"純發洩 發完再繼續抗爭"},{"pid":"32b1d0191d681e55db1926744068401a9034474e","tid":1735442,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":